D   |23             |850              |3.05                 |75.8                  |Medium (20-39)|\n|St. Louis       |MO   |17             |1086             |3.83                 |81.8                  |Low (10-19)   |\n|New Orleans     |LA   |13             |2262             |4.0                  |206.1                 |Low (10-19)   |\n|Carmel          |IN   |11             |291              |3.6                  |90.6                  |Low (10-19)   |\n|Clearwater      |FL   |10             |679              |3.3                  |80.1                  |Low (10-19)   |\n|St Louis        |MO   |9              |150              |3.58                 |129.9                 |Minimal (<10) |\n|Santa Barbara   |CA   |9              |1534             |3.83                 |206.3                 |Minimal (<10) |\n|Sparks          |NV   |9              |334              |3.41                 |114.4                 |Minimal (<10) |\n|Saint Petersburg|FL   |9              |491              |3.61                 |103.9                 |Minimal (<10) |\n|Newark          |DE   |8              |146              |3.21                 |65.0                  |Minimal (<10) |\n|King Of Prussia |PA   |8              |191              |3.15                 |111.3                 |Minimal (<10) |\n|Franklin        |TN   |8              |442              |3.43                 |83.1                  |Minimal (<10) |\n|Cherry Hill     |NJ   |8              |594              |3.41                 |80.6                  |Minimal (<10) |\n|Greenwood       |IN   |8              |207              |3.29                 |50.8                  |Minimal (<10) |\n+----------------+-----+---------------+-----------------+---------------------+----------------------+--------------+\nonly showing top 20 rows\n\n"},{"type":"TABLE","data":"city_clean\tstate\tstarbucks_count\ttotal_restaurants\tavg_restaurant_rating\treviews_per_restaurant\tstarbucks_tier\nTucson\tAZ\t59\t2473\t2.9\t96.7\tHigh (40+)\nI